        .container
            h2.section__title About
            p.section__paragraph.
                I am a Computer Science student at Aberystwyth University, currently on a placement year working as a web developer for <a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news">BBC News</a> in London.
            p.section__paragraph.
                I am a foolish dreamer in love with code, video games and good coffee.
            p.section__paragraph.
                This site was built by hand, from scratch, not only as a way to showcase some of the work I've done, but also as a learning exercise, allowing me to play and experiment, and practice my front-end development skills. It uses the <a href="https://pugjs.org/">pug</a> template language, is styled with <a href="http://sass-lang.com/">Sass</a>, and transpiles ES2015+ to ES5 with <a href="https://babeljs.io/">Babel</a>. The source for this site can be found on <a href="https://github.com/punit-shah/punit-shah.github.io">Github</a>.

